				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">on half the right click items in game?  I mean sure, I can see why you would need to equip boots of bladecalling and burning scepter of elements, thats fine...
<br />

<br />
But I got a shield of auras a few days ago, thinking, "woot, rune", but I never realised how much of an absolute pain in the ass the thing is, I have to dig it out of my bag, swap, click, if I get hit, I have to do it again.  Why are things like this not clickable from inventory? It wouldn't be overpowering, it'd just stop annoyance in the game... There's a lot of items like this, such as ornate legs, flowers of functionality, shrink devices (seriously... wtf).
<br />

<br />
I have no idea why some of these items are flagged must equip... hell, I dont even know why i'm posting ~ bye.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=339789" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://mywebpages.comcast.net/vicour1/AnduranSig.jpg" border="0" /></a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
